<h1>描述</h1>

<p>请注意, 这 <strong>实际上是一道提交答案题</strong>.</p>

<p>王保保是一名侦探, 最擅长侦破高智商的犯罪, 在坏人的"罪恶都市"群中有着极大的名声.</p>

<p>终于有一天, 有着鬼才之称的代号为X的坏人忍不住了, 想尽一切办法把王保保抓了起来, 捆在了一张椅子上, 然后拿出了十张纸, 上面有十个谜题, 然后告诉他:"这里有十个谜题, 每个谜题只有提示的线索以及对应的密文, 你需要根据线索和密文找出相应的答案, 如果不能在规定时间内解出来, 那么, 你就会被嘿嘿嘿!"</p>

<p>王保保还很年轻, 他可不想被坏人干掉, 于是启动了通灵之术, 找到了在考场上的你, 请你帮他尽量多的破解谜题, 来帮助他脱离困境.</p>

<h1>格式</h1>

<h2>输入格式</h2>

<p>数据被依次编号为 1 到 10, 其中每一组数据的输入文件中都只有一个整数, 恰好就是这一组数据的编号.</p>

<h2>输出格式</h2>

<p>对于输入的编号, 输出其对应的结果即可. </p>

<h1>数据信息</h1>

<h2>1.in</h2>

<p>Find the sum of the first 5 terms (mod 1000000123) of the hidden sequence inside the following string.<br>
12345678......</p>

<h2>2.in</h2>

<p>Find the sum of the first 15 terms (mod 1000000123) of the hidden sequence inside the following string.<br>
1234567891929394959697989995591928777......</p>

<h2>3.in</h2>

<p>Find the sum of the first 500 terms (mod 1000000123) of the hidden sequence inside the following string.<br>
......</p>

<h2>4.in</h2>

<p>Find the sum of the first 100000000000000 terms (mod 1000000123) of the hidden sequence inside the following string.<br>
1234567899192939495969798999919929939949959969979989999991......</p>

<h2>5.in</h2>

<p>Find the sum of the first 100000000000000 terms (mod 1000000123) of the hidden sequence inside the following string.<br>
1234567891929394959697989991992993994995996997998999991999......</p>

<h2>6.in</h2>

<p>Find the sum of the first 100000000000000 terms (mod 1000000123) of the hidden sequence inside the following string.<br>
1234567895556666777788889996676777777787888888898999997777......</p>

<h2>7.in</h2>

<p>Find the sum of the first 100000000000000 terms (mod 1000000123) of the hidden sequence inside the following string.<br>
1111111111111111111111111111111111111111111111111111111111......</p>

<h2>8.in</h2>

<p>Find the sum of the first 100000000000000 terms (mod 1000000123) of the hidden sequence inside the following string.<br>
121212121212121212121212121212121212121212121212121212121212......</p>

<h2>9.in</h2>

<p>Find the sum of the first 100000000000000 terms (mod 1000000123) of the hidden sequence inside the following string.<br>
1234321234321234321234321234321234321234321234321234321234321......</p>

<h2>10.in</h2>

<p>Find the sum of the first 100000000000000 terms (mod 1000000123) of the hidden sequence inside the following string.<br>
111322311132231113223111322311132231113223111322311132231113223111322311132231113223......</p>

<h1>限制</h1>

<p>1s</p>
